#: ../../D/Don-t-do-that-then-.rst:5
msgid "Don't do that then!"
msgstr "Don't do that then!"

#: ../../D/Don-t-do-that-then-.rst:7
msgid "imp\\."
msgstr "命令法"

#: ../../D/Don-t-do-that-then-.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from an old doctor's office joke about a patient with a trivial complaint] "
"Stock response to a user complaint. \"When I type control-S, the whole "
"system comes to a halt for thirty seconds.\" \"Don't do that, then!\" (or "
"\"So don't do that!\"). Compare :ref:`RTFM`\\."
msgstr ""
"[ささいな訴えを抱えた患者についての古い医院の小話から] ユーザーの苦情に対する決まり文句の応答。「control-"
"Sをタイプすると、システム全体が30秒間止まってしまうんだ。」「じゃあそれをやらなきゃいい!」(または「だからそれをやるなって!」)。\\ "
":ref:`RTFM`\\ と比較せよ。"

#: ../../D/Don-t-do-that-then-.rst:15
msgid ""
"Here's a classic example of \"Don't do that then!\" from Neal Stephenson's "
"*In The Beginning Was The Command Line*\\. A friend of his built a network "
"with a load of Macs and a few high-powered database servers. He found that "
"from time to time the whole network would lock up for no apparent reason. "
"The problem was eventually tracked down to MacOS's cooperative multitasking:"
" when a user held down the mouse button for too long, the network stack "
"wouldn't get a chance to run..."
msgstr ""
"Neal Stephensonの『*In The Beginning Was The Command Line*』にある、「Don't do that "
"then!」の古典的な例を紹介しよう。彼の友人が、大量のMacと数台の高性能データベースサーバーでネットワークを構築した。彼は、時折ネットワーク全体が明白な理由もなくロックアップすることに気づいた。問題は最終的に、MacOSの協調的マルチタスクに突き止められた。ユーザーがマウスボタンを長く押しすぎると、ネットワークスタックが実行される機会を得られなかったのだ……。"
